replyTime":"2020-07-11T15:06:02.000Z","msg":"今日有唔少人因為條是非題中咗伏，又有唔少人唔識搵票站編碼，所以都係出返個簡單懶人包，入到票站直接比QR Code 同住址證明 1 分鐘就搞掂<br />\n<br />\n- 官方投票網址係 <a href=\"https://webapp.popvote.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwebapp.popvote.hk&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyDcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=c33bf808\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://webapp.popvote.hk</a><br />\n- 票站編號而家可以上 <a href=\"https://legco2020.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegco2020.com&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyDcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=6170a016\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://legco2020.com</a> 查，但都係以官方 Excel 為準，可以同票站人員確認 (<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/&hellip;/1rTHp9g2UfTax1rQMgJEyQ6CEjH&hellip;/view\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2F%E2%80%A6%2F1rTHp9g2UfTax1rQMgJEyQ6CEjH%E2%80%A6%2Fview&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyDcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=1d7f74ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/&hellip;/1rTHp9g2UfTax1rQMgJEyQ6CEjH&hellip;/view</a>)<br />\n- 超區選民一定要喺 #果條是非題 答「否」<br />\n- 填到最後見到 QR code，先帶埋住址證明入票站確認<br />\n<br />\n（咩話？仲未諗掂揀邊個？ 即上 <a href=\"https://legco2020.com/candidates\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegco2020.com%2Fcandidates&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyDcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=941a012c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://legco2020.com/candidates</a>)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o7HO9WN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo7HO9WN.png&h=457d15db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb990f395bc28ed24d5dfad5ed74cdfd1a7e1da9","tid":2103993,"uid":228337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T15:07:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb0d3d2cecd453b4176cd089cc99208c45eefcc3","tid":2103993,"uid":226588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T15:07:40.000Z","msg":"推"}